Requirements
---

GCC

A GNU-compatible make utility

Allegro, version 4.2 or higher
Get it from http://alleg.sourceforge.net


Building it
---

Just type 'make' and follow the instructions.  If it fails for whatever
reason, drop me a line at stainless@users.sourceforge.net.


Optional packages
---

AllegroGL (requires OpenGL and GLU)
Get it at http://allegrogl.sourceforge.net

HawkNL
Get it at http://www.hawksoft.com

OpenAL and freealut
Get it at http://www.openal.org

zlib
Get it at http://www.gzip.org/zlib
